an>&#x27; ｝｝ /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Thumbnail</span> <span class="attr">source</span>=<span class="string">｛｛uri:</span> &#x27;<span class="attr">https:</span>//<span class="attr">steemitimages.com</span>/<span class="attr">u</span>/<span class="attr">jacobyu</span>/<span class="attr">avatar</span>&#x27; ｝｝ /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Thumbnail</span> <span class="attr">source</span>=<span class="string">｛｛uri:</span> &#x27;<span class="attr">https:</span>//<span class="attr">steemitimages.com</span>/<span class="attr">u</span>/<span class="attr">blockchainstudio</span>/<span class="attr">avatar</span>&#x27; ｝｝ /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Thumbnail</span> <span class="attr">source</span>=<span class="string">｛｛uri:</span> &#x27;<span class="attr">https:</span>//<span class="attr">steemitimages.com</span>/<span class="attr">u</span>/<span class="attr">gomdory</span>/<span class="attr">avatar</span>&#x27; ｝｝ /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Thumbnail</span> <span class="attr">source</span>=<span class="string">｛｛uri:</span> &#x27;<span class="attr">https:</span>//<span class="attr">steemitimages.com</span>/<span class="attr">u</span>/<span class="attr">bbooaae</span>/<span class="attr">avatar</span>&#x27; ｝｝ /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Thumbnail</span> <span class="attr">source</span>=<span class="string">｛｛uri:</span> &#x27;<span class="attr">https:</span>//<span class="attr">steemitimages.com</span>/<span class="attr">u</span>/<span class="attr">codingman</span>/<span class="attr">avatar</span>&#x27; ｝｝ /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Thumbnail</span> <span class="attr">source</span>=<span class="string">｛｛uri:</span> &#x27;<span class="attr">https:</span>//<span class="attr">steemitimages.com</span>/<span class="attr">u</span>/<span class="attr">bukio</span>/<span class="attr">avatar</span>&#x27; ｝｝ /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ScrollView</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">View</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">View</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">｛/* 여기까지 스토리 헤더 끝 */｝</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Thumbnail</strong> 에는 제 팔로우 친구들의 사진을 임의로 가져와서 출력하였습니다.</p>
</blockquote>
<br>
<p>여기까지 작업한 화면입니다. 피드 상단에 팔로우 친구들이 보입니다.</p>
<p><img alt data-src="https://cdn.steemitimages.com/300x0/https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3969643/51506135-06079580-1e2e-11e9-973a-b25b1a3fb3cb.png"></p>
